// Layers 0-9
//------------
//  0 (Far BG)
//  1 (Med BG)
//  2 (Close BG)
//  3 (Near BG 1)
//  4 (Near BG 2)
//  5 ("Here")
//  6 (Near FG 1)
//  7 (Near FG 2)
//  8 (Close FG)
//  9 (Far FG)

// Presets:
//----------

// Mcodes (map codes):
// 0 - draw only
// 1 - place solid platform

// Light types:
// -1 (off, none)
// 0 -

// Object types:
// -1 (none)
// 0 -

// Key bindings for editor:
// H - show help
// C - Random Color
// W - set to white
// R / G / B - turn off a channel
// R / G / B & Shift/Ctrl (+) and (-) manipulate color, A=alpha, E=blend
// X - Toggle "exclusive mode" (shows only active layer)
// O - Onion Mode (Toggles display onion-skinning of non-active layers)
// Q - Toggle Auto-Rotation of Tile Painter
// S - make tile solid
// MWUp/MWDown - Change Tile
// T - select tileset
// Z - select tween
// V - select light type
// J - select add light at position with current color
// K - remove light from tile
// Insert - Add a "precisely located light"
// Delete - Removes last added light
// Home   - Place an object at the current position
// End    - Remove the last object added
// F2 - Save
// F3 - Load
// Keypad Asterisk - Reads drawColor,Code,Alpha,Blend and Tileset into pen
// I - select object to draw onto tiles
// U - remove any object on the tile
// P - place an object on the tile
// Y - places object2

